# linkedin-post-generator — IntelliForge AI
# Share Your Training Experience → LinkedIn Post
# Built by BuildwithAiGiri x IntelliForge AI — https://www.intelliforge.tech/

Stack: Next.js 14 App Router / TypeScript / Tailwind / better-sqlite3 / OpenRouter
Colors: #7c3aed (purple-primary) | #00d4ff (cyan-accent) | #030014 (dark-bg)
Admin: /admin — share analytics (no auth in MVP)
API: POST /api/generate — AI post gen | POST+GET /api/shares — tracking

Branding rules:
- Always link to https://learning.intelliforge.tech in generated posts
- Always mention "IntelliForge AI" in post copy
- Footer must credit IntelliForge AI + BuildwithAiGiri
